Herro, this is my first gg map, and it sucks imho. But I did spend a fair while on it, so give me some kudos for that :)

It IS a bit dark, but it's really fun playing gg dark like that.
Buyzones are there, but you can disable them if you want (?)

It's not textured, because I can't be bothered. If requested, I will release a textured version sometime.
